---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutImg from "../assets/bg-molecules.webp";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section>
    <div class="header">
      <Image src={aboutImg} alt="" class="img" />
      <h1>About NeuroImpact Therapeutics</h1>
    </div>
    <h2>Transforming Lives Through Targeted Therapeutics</h2>
    <p>
      At NeuroImpact Therapeutics, we are dedicated to transforming the lives of
      patients suffering from neurological disorders by pioneering the
      development of targeted, precision-driven therapeutics.
    </p>

    <h2>Advancing Ion Channels Research</h2>
    <p>
      By leveraging cutting-edge structural biology and a deep understanding of
      ion channels and disease-associated proteins, we aim to unlock novel
      pathways for treating debilitating conditions such as Alzheimerâ€™s and
      epilepsy.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our mission is to bridge innovation and impact, delivering groundbreaking
      solutions that address unmet medical needs and restore hope to patients
      and their families.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Vision for Neurological Disorder Treatment</h2>
    <p>
      Our vision is to revolutionize the treatment of neurological disorders,
      enabling a future where effective therapeutics improve lives worldwide.
    </p>

    <h2>Core Values</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>Innovation:</strong> Driving breakthroughs in science and medicine.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Collaboration:</strong> Partnering with researchers and institutions
        to accelerate progress.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Patient-Centric Approach:</strong> Focusing on improving lives and
        addressing unmet medical needs.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Scientific Excellence:</strong> Leveraging cutting-edge research
        and expertise.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Call for Partnership</h2>
    <p>
      We welcome collaborations with academic institutions, industry leaders,
      and investors who share our passion for advancing neurological health.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>
      At NeuroImpact Therapeutics, we are committed to making a meaningful
      impact on the lives of patients, families, and the broader medical
      community. Together, we can change the future of neurological care.
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    .header {
      position: relative;
      /* overflow: hidden; */
      min-height: 30vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .header img {
      position: absolute;
      width: 500px;
      height: auto;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    h1::after {
      content: "";
      background: linear-gradient(
        to right,
        var(--clr-gradient-start),
        var(--clr-gradient-end)
      );
      width: 80%;
      height: 2px;
      position: absolute;
      top: 100%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 3rem);
      margin-block-end: 20px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--clr-gradient-start);
      width: fit-content;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
    }
    ul li {
      margin-block-end: 10px;
    }
    ul li strong {
      color: var(--clr-gradient-end);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
